<br>
<i>Although an infiltrator has more spec points, neither the Inf nor the NS will likely take their envenom past 39.</i><br>
<br>
Yes, and then the infiltrator can either improve their weapon skill or their dual wield. The first choice will slightly improve their damage output. The second choice will slightly improve their damage output and increase the chance of applying both poisons.<br>
<br>
